name: Global X High Interest Savings ETF
longDescription: To achieve its investment objective, CASH invests substantially all of its assets in high interest deposit accounts with one  or more Canadian chartered banks. CASH may also invest in high-quality, short-term debt securities, including treasury bills and promissory notes issued or guaranteed by Canadian governments or their agencies, and bankers acceptances. CASH will not engage in securities lending. CASH seeks to maximize monthly income for unitholders while preserving capital and liquidity by investing primarily in high interest deposit accounts with Canadian banks.
